claim.claim-text:
Method of formation of a polymer-based foam composition as defined in any of claims 1 to 11, comprising:
a) providing a polymer composition;
b) providing a microcrystalline talc product;
c) introducing the microcrystalline talc product into the polymer composition in an extrusion-mixing process; and
d) foaming the polymer composition using a gas such as CO2, nitrogen or a noble gas.
